awesome! i'm at the starting point

empenzando con el mapa
¡claro! ¿me dirijo a la isla del tigre o me quedo donde estoy?
ve en medio de la tigre y la rama
genial, estoy en medio de la tigre y la rama

preferies ingles o espanol?
no problem, english works great too

From the middle, go below the rock below the tiger. bout an inch

what's the next move, friend?
from there move to the top of the branch on your left. Let me know when you reach the branch

follow the branch to the island with the parrot

what's my next step, pal?
Stop by the rocks connecting to the island with the frog

cross the rocks going through the middle into the isnland with the frog
awesome! i've crossed the rocks and now i'm on the island with the frog
is the frog to your right?
yup, the frog is on my right side
go south until you are parrarel to the frogs top-left leg. Its only a couple inches

si

ayi estory
perfecto
now cross the path and head towards the flower stand. But, don't get to the flower stand!
ok im there

im at the top right corner
perfecto! cruza ahora sobre la ramita y sigue hacia abajo
verás a otro perro blanco junto a un mantel de picnic a cuadros
i cross the log

Now continue heading left
im north of the mantel

next to the basket

im below the flowers next to the bike
estás haciendo un gran trabajo! ahora, da un paso a la izquierda, ve debajo del florista y sigue hacia el gran puente, verás a dos personas andando en bicicleta

estupendo! sóplemente pasado el puente encontraras un banquito con dos ancianitos leyendo
move south, between the grandparents and the wooden twig

fantástico! ahora, sigue el camino hacia el este, entre el arbusto y la ramita, va mosvasías!

go south between the cliff to right and the dog to left until you reach the path
cool, i see the dog and the cliff. heading south now

from there follow the path east until you reach the fire. stay on the grass but as close to path as possible
routing east, moving along the path, staying on the grass
i can see the fire now. what's next, amigo?
go around the fire by traveling above it until you reach the path again
Bien entendido, rodeando el fuego para volver a incorporarnos al camino.
go east until the mushroom
on it, heading east towards the mushroom
i see the red mushroom. what's next, buddy?
go east under the mushroom
Muy bien, pasando por debajo del hongo, en dirección este.
are you above the car?
nope, i'm under the mushroom
where to now?
move east until you are above the car
Lo tengo, moviéndome hacia el este hasta que esté encima del auto.
cross the road westward. do not touch the car. You should be above the hood of the car
gotcha, crossing westward, not touching the car, now i'm above the hood
follow the path until you reach the telescope. stop right above it
sure thing, mate! following the path to the telescope and stopping above it
go around the telescope using the eastern side until you stop below the telescope and above the tree
got it, going around the telescope on the east side, stopping below it and above the tree
¿que sigue?
go south between the tree and telescope
hecho, voy al sur entre el árbol y el telescopio
reach the path
righteo! i'm back on the path
what's next, pal?
follow the path westward under the telescope until you reach the turn. stop before the turn
Muy bien, dirigiéndonos hacia el oeste bajo el telescopio hasta la curva del camino, deteniéndonos antes del giro.
go westward to the cabin. go between where the two rock formations meet. its at a 45 degree angle above you
alrighty, going westward to the cabin, passing betwixt the spot where two rock formations meet
it's at a 45 degree angle above me. let's do this!
enter the cabin
entering the cabin now

hi there! que comience el juego!!
listo

Before reaching the third palm tree, turn left and continue south. you got it?
im bewteen the two left most palm trees above the dog. where should I head?
awesome, now spot the cute brown puppy
Gire un poco hacia la izquierda y luego gire rápidamente a la derecha en dirección sur. ¡al trote!
no ententito

im to the left of the dog

then, turn right and follow the water line along the big rock. keep going west

head west towards the big rock

super! now, continue along the water until you reach a medium rock
after that, you're going to say hello to our friend, the shark!

great job! now, let's get dry again

si
go north my friend, just a bit further!
im below the speaker

now, head south towards the sea

keep it going!
